Breakdown/Hiss/Pyro/Double Punch/Punch:



Breakdown saw a fast moving car dodging through the trees, heading towards 
Dinobot and Tavatron, and this vehicle was a Maximal.  He couldn't allow that!

Raising his weapon, he fired off a grenade at Dinobot's buttocks, which is 
really the only part he could see through the trees.  "Take out the Maximal!"

Hiss, a little confused, opened fire on Tavatron from behind with a single 
fusion blast, not knowing WHICH Maximal that idiot Breakdown was talking 
about.

Pyro continued lighting the forest up on fire, two more fireballs exploding 
against two more trees, the fire spreading very fast.

Punch fired off three plasma blasts from his plasma cannon off at Hot Rod, 
running as fast as his servos would allow.

---

Double Punch stopped, running through the forest now, charging forward, 
firing off a missile at Hot Rod, not uttering a word, still in his cloak 
mode.  Though, do to damage, it had a fringe effect.
